After that I go to my customers outlet. Majority of my merchandise are snack, only a little of beverage, sometimes  bring some little toys too. Most of my customers market segment are children. Because the children have high frequency for buying them. In the afternoon  I come back to my boarding house, because I do not have  house. Every month  I pay a rent fee.Tomorrow morning I go to my friend's store for calculation how much the merchandise I brought yesterday sold, then I pay to my friend a sum of merchandise sold. I might take again some merchandise I need.
